text: Sajjad Doraji () is an Iranian Football Forward who currently plays for Iranian football club Naft Masjed Soleyman in the Iran Pro League. ==Club career== Doraji started his career with youth academies in Ahvaz. He was part Foolad U19 during 2011–12 season. He also captained Naft Ahvaz U21 in 2013–14 Iranian U21 Premier League.
